  <section id="Section518989">
    <title><anchor id="Anchor919483" role="Index"
    xreflabel="planner codes:assigning items to;items:assigning to planner codes" />
    <indexterm significance="normal" zone="Anchor919483">
        <primary>planner codes</primary>

        <secondary>assigning items to</secondary>
      </indexterm> <indexterm significance="normal" zone="Anchor919483">
        <primary>items</primary>

        <secondary>assigning to planner codes</secondary>
      </indexterm>Assign Item to Planner Code</title>

    <para id="Para524455">To assign an Item to a Planner Code, select the
    "Assign Item to Planner Code" option. The following screen will
    appear:</para>

    <para id="Para524458"><screenshot>
        <mediaobject>
          <imageobject>
            <imagedata fileref="images/PO_Utils_assignItemPCode.png"
                       id="Graphic524464" />
          </imageobject>

          <caption id="Caption524477">Assign Item to Planner Code</caption>
        </mediaobject>
      </screenshot></para>

    <para id="Para524488">When assigning an Item to a Planner Code, you are
    presented with the following options:</para>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para524491">Item Number</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x18dc574">
          <para>Enter the Item Number of the Item you want to assign to a
          Planner Code.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry role="openmfg">
        <term id="Para524499">All Warehouses</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x18dc598">
          <para>Select to assign the Item to a Planner Code for all
          Warehouses.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry role="openmfg">
        <term id="Para524501">Selected</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x18dc5bc">
          <para>Specify Warehouse where you want to assign the Item to a
          Planner Code.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para524521">Planner Code</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x18dc604">
          <para>Specify the Planner Code you want to assign the Item
          to.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>

    <para id="Para524530">To the far right of the screen, the following
    buttons are available:</para>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para524531">CANCEL</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x18dc670">
          <para>Closes the screen without assigning an Item to a Planner Code,
          returning you to the application desktop.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para524532">ASSIGN</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x18dc6b8">
          <para>Assigns the specified Item to the specified Planner
          Code.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
  </section>